          explanation: 'Taking moments about the right support (B): R_A × 10 = 15 × (10-2) + 25 × (10-7) = 15 × 8 + 25 × 3 = 120 + 75 = 195. Therefore R_A = 195/10 = 19.5 kN. Verification: R_B = (15 + 25) - 19.5 = 20.5 kN. Check moment about A: 20.5(10) - 15(2) - 25(7) = 205 - 30 - 175 = 0. Correct.',
